snippet.title: Gumshoe Complete Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A beginning to end playthrough of Nintendo's 1986 light gun platformer, Gumshoe from http://www.nintendocomplete.com

This is a really cool innovation on the Zapper game - it's a platform game that requires you to control the main character with nothing more than the light gun. You shoot him to make him jump, and shoot obstacles to clear the way. For a game that's so short, this one takes a loooooooong time to get all the way through.
_______________
